movie.title: Breakthrough
movie.plot: Tragedy strikes when a woman named Joyce's son falls through the ice on a frozen lake and is trapped underwater for over 15 minutes. After being rushed to the hospital, the 14-year-old boy continues to fight for his life as Joyce, her husband and their pastor stay by his bedside and pray for a miracle.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 2 wins & 10 nominations.
